The '''1998 [[Victory Bowl]]''', the second edition of the annual game, was a [[college football]] [[bowl game]] played on Saturday, November 27, 1999, at [[Fawcett Stadium]] in [[Canton, Ohio]]. It featured the [[MidAmerica Nazarene University|MidAmerica Nazarene Pioneers]] against the [[Geneva College|Geneva Golden Tornadoes]]. The Tornadoes won 31&ndash;26.
