'''Chinese Taipei Chess Association''' (中華民國西洋棋協會) is the [[Sport governing body|governing body]] for [[chess]] in the [[Republic of China|Republic of China, (Taiwan)]]. It is a member of the [[Chinese Taipei Olympic Committee]]. It is based in [[Taipei, Taiwan]]. Joined [[FIDE]] in 2004 (Zone 3.3).

*President: Szu-Chuen TSAI ([http://www.fide.com/component/content/article/4-tournaments/1805-296-new-president-of-chinese-taipei-chess-association appointed in 2007])
*General Secretary: Ko-Fei LIU

