[[Image:Logo of the FEC.png|thumb|FEC logo]]
The '''Ecuadorian Cycling Federation''' or '''FEC''' (in [[Spanish language|Spanish]]: ''Federación Ecuatoriana de Ciclismo'') is the national [[sport governing body|governing body]] of [[bicycle racing|cycle racing]] in [[Ecuador]].

The FEC is a member of the [[Union Cycliste Internationale|UCI]] and [[Confederacion Panamericana de Ciclismo|COPACI]].

