'''Emiliano Té''' (born April 15, 1983 in [[Bissau]]) is a [[Guinea Bissau|Bissau-Guinean]] [[Association football|football]] [[midfielder]], who plays for [[GD Coruchense]] in the Portuguese lower divisions.
He played mostly in Portugal, but also played briefly for Chinese club [[Yanbian FC]] in 2008.
He holds [[Portugal|Portuguese]] nationality.
